¿Estás bien?

00:24:31.730 --> 00:24:32.530
Señor Chu.

00:24:35.330 --> 00:24:36.160
Siyu.

00:24:38.860 --> 00:24:40.730
Te he molestado estos días.

00:24:46.120 --> 00:24:46.960
Señor Chu.

